commitResults.messageTitle: Level 0: Changed name to Bob, Added skeletal version
Level 2: Implemented TaskList with add and list
Level 3: Implemented Task class, Implemented Mark as done
Level 4: Added ToDo, Deadline & Event. Updated the rest of code accordingly
Bob A-TextUiTesting: Automated Text UI Testing
A-Enums: Implemented using Enums instead for TaskType and Command Type
Task.java: Updated access modifiers, abstract class, save format
commitResults.messageBody:
Updated access modifiers to protected to allow subclasses todo, deadline
& event to access super class variables

Implemented save format
|<Type>|<isDone>|<desc>|<deadline/from>|<to>

Implemented saving and loading of savedtasks files.

Saving:
If parent directory DNE, create parent directory

Loading:
If file DNE, uses empty tasklist
Else reads each line within file and populates tasklist accordingly

DeadlineTask now stores variable by as a LocalDate.

All by related logic now done within DeadlineTask instead of its
superclass Task. i.e. parsing of DateTime format

commitResults.messageTitle: Level 8: Updated EventTask.java to use datetime
commitResults.messageBody:
EventTask from and to now variables are now LocalDates

Like DeadlineTask, it catches DateTimeParseException

Cleaned up Bob.java, removed unnecesary try catch

Implemented more Exceptions for more specific error handling
BobDateTimeException: Handles DateTime logic errors i.e. to < from
BobInvalidFormatException: Handles Invalid Format when using Commands
Updated Tasks (and all subclasses) and Tasklist to handle new exceptions

Created CommandFormat enum for easy accessing of command formats

Updated All applicable tasks to use correct datetime format

Updated testing files to accurately reflect updated code
